name: Inside out
description:
Have you ever turned your attention inwards? This is what introspection is about. It's about observing the inside of yourself instead of looking at the outside world. It's as if the world is being seen from the inside out!

Gear I used
Camera: Nikon FM10 
Lens: 35~70 1:3.5~4.8 
Film: Fujicolor C200

Technique: Double Exposure
